I am using Slackware 2.0.0 on a home-brewed system consisting of a
P90 (Intel "Plato" MB) + a #9 GXE64pro + a NCR 53c8xx controller. Works
great.

X only works in 16 colours (using the VGA server), but XFree 3.1 will
contain support for the #9 chip.

If there is anything else you need to know, feel free to ask.

